headline: Homes.com Report: National home price appreciation strengthens in November
summary: ARLINGTON, Va., December 11, 2025--Homes.com, a CoStar Group leading online residential marketplace, released a new report today analyzing home price trends in November, including details across major metros and house types.

headline: US retailers buy up real estate again as market tightens
summary: Retailers in the United States are stepping up their search for store locations as demand for physical retail space outpaces supply.
